{"tid":1764568,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【生態災難之謎】抗爭期間死4600隻雀 漁護署：少有文獻提及催淚氣體影響","createTime":"2019-12-01T07:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T10:46:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a62624245ad5fe6e41c36b1c819062be1d918b0c","tid":1764568,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"近月，不斷有市民發現街上雀鳥屍橫遍野，懷疑催淚彈殺雀的控訴此起彼落，可惜一直未有相關專家能給出雀鳥死因的確實定案。現時香港的野鳥屍體集中由漁護署收集及處理，本報向漁護署查詢過往數月的雀鳥死亡數字，獲漁護署回覆指2019年6月至11月28日期間，確實檢獲的雀鳥屍體數量達4668隻。<br />\n<br />\n香港野生雀鳥受香港法例第170章《野生動物保護條例》保護，任何人除非得到特別許可，不得管有任何已死亡的野生動物屍體，因此只有漁護署，才會有確切的野生雀鳥死亡數據。過去三年，漁護署每年檢獲的雀鳥屍體均上達萬隻，當中部份會由漁護署轄下的大龍獸醫化驗所進行化驗，但主要是要掌握禽流感情況。2018年漁護署檢獲的10777隻雀鳥屍體中，就有4472隻進行了禽流感測試。<br />\n<br />\n但除禽流感外，對於每隻雀鳥的個別死因，漁護署指因為野鳥在野外死亡的原因眾多，而且屍體發現時可能已有若干程度的分解，不易找出確實的死亡原因。至於市民猜測的催淚氣體殺雀，漁護署則僅回覆指「催淚氣體對動物産生的影響視乎品種、接觸到催淚氣體的時間長短及濃度，不能一概而論，現時少有科學文獻有關催淚氣體對野鳥的影響」。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署表示會密切留意本港野鳥情況，如發現有大量野鳥不尋常死亡，會作出調查。就此，香港有保育團體呼籲市民幫助蒐證，收集雀鳥死亡數據： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/37RuVXx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37RuVXx&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B3wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=d8768e23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/37RuVXx</a> 。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191201/large/1575172275_d525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575172275_d525.jpg&h=7d75c5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191201/60329861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60329861&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B3wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=7b48a908\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60329861&h=e4b1ab4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191201/60329861</a>"},{"pid":"257036a7e36860070508462c3bf1f6896783fbaf","tid":1764568,"uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"山埃殺雀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebca1d14e542f5e3088ab5fb433d47e92d2560a","tid":1764568,"uid":522,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"叫漁護署班人唔帶mask 去示威現場聞下tear gas 有幾大影到未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11dde94e2e4baa378f8706ca050078b25a5b091e","tid":1764568,"uid":7860,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:57:18.000Z","msg":"緊係少有文獻啦 邊有地方好似香港放tg 放得咁撚癲<br />\n人都死 何況咁細隻雀"},{"pid":"8d650a120dee7b40850e3647e607c43122c49175","tid":1764568,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:58:55.000Z","msg":"毅進Sir：暴徒燒雜物的影響更大"},{"pid":"91b293c25f5c47e97de8c2cf32c0f834bb72f571","tid":1764568,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"257036a7e36860070508462c3bf1f6896783fbaf","tid":1764568,"uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"山埃殺雀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYGzWYe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYGzWYe.png&h=0a68347d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pwrc.usgs.gov/eisler/CHR_23_Cyanide.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pwrc.usgs.gov%2Feisler%2FCHR_23_Cyanide.pdf&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B3wORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=d0ff9549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pwrc.usgs.gov/eisler/CHR_23_Cyanide.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"46b2d0e5d07b10f0330d4b3921924e492bc42b8b","tid":1764568,"uid":26385,